snippet.title: 60 Seconds to escape !
snippet.description:
Project for the Novice Summer Jam Series 2024: Mini jam 2

Link : https://leadcreep.itch.io/60-seconds-to-escape
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

Jam Team :

DELCROIX Victor :
 - https://leadcreep.itch.io/
- https://github.com/LeadCreep

BRISSY Axel :
- https://oneblack74.itch.io/                 
- https://github.com/oneblack74

MACKOWIAK Carole :
- https://vailwyn.itch.io/    
- https://github.com/Carole-prog
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

You are trapped in an escape room, the timer is counting down, you only have one minute to escape the room !
Find clues and note them down, the room resets but not the note pad ! Keep it up, I have faith in you !
